			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Get some levels, and start pulling some LDoN's.  Nothing screams Good Barding like making your group go &quot;wow, the mobs just kept coming and we kept beating em down.  That was awesome!&quot;  It takes a little practice, but it's really not hard at all.  You'll get it down eventually.  And if you have any questions, or need more help about how to do stuff, there are great guides here and awesome people to make fun of you as they help you.</span></td>
