				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Not sure what role I'm supposed to be filling<a name="57108"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 17 04 11:58 AM</span></td>
