 Second of all, you came to the right place.  Most people know little about bards like the enchanter you grouped with.  You really need to know the class well to pull your wieght.
<br />

<br />
 You are really at a low spot for bard power at 56, soloing you are a god but your group buffs arent all that great.  A lot of cool stuff opens up later (fade, WoZ, PoV, Overhaste/focus, HoS) that increases bard power 10 fold.
<br />

<br />
 Read the boards here and find out what you have to look foward to.
<br />

<br />
  On a side note.  If you ever feel underpowered do LDoNs  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
Just wanted to add, enchanter mez and bard mez STACK.  Not only does bard mez not overwrite enchanter mez, but they stack.
<br />

<br />
 An easy test, have both mez a mob then charm the mob, 2 icon will be up (good way to shut up bad enchanters)</span></td>
