				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Not sure what role I'm supposed to be filling<a name="57253"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 18 04 4:22 AM</span></td>
