				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Not sure what role I'm supposed to be filling<a name="57400"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 18 04 7:18 PM</span></td>
